==地理==
[[File:Daley_Plaza_060716.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:One_Summer_Night_in_the_Windy_City.jpg|thumb]]
根據[[美國2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，庫克縣總面積為{{convert|1635|sqmi|1}}。其中有{{convert|946|sqmi|1}}，即57.84%為陸地；{{convert|689|sqmi|1}}，即42.16%為水域。庫克縣的最高點為其西北角，海拔約1,000英尺。<ref>[http://www.isgs.uiuc.edu/maps-data-pub/cook-atlas/topo.shtml ISGS - Topography of Cook County] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105195155/http://www.isgs.uiuc.edu/maps-data-pub/cook-atlas/topo.shtml |date=2013-01-05 }}</ref>

